creator: Koelnmesse GmbH
descriptionHtml:
The Mobile Guide for Kind + Jugend is the interactive event guide for the event from Kind + Jugend 09.–11.09.2021

At Kind + Jugend Re-Start Edition you will find a selection of manufacturers who deliberately want to stage their innovations and highlights as a new start for the industry. And who are convinced of their ideas and concepts. Let yourself be inspired and take your time for the most beautiful and promising products that can lead your business into a successful future. And of course our Trend Forum will provide you with the most important industry trends and market overviews and give you valuable impulses for your everyday business. We're glad you're here to welcome the re-start of Kind + Jugend with us.

The international leading trade fair for premium baby and toddler products is the perfect platform for global commerce and the order business. In no other place in the world can one see so much of what will already be in children's rooms tomorrow.

EXHIBITOR | PRODUCTS | INFORMATIONS

The app offers a detailed exhibitor and product directory as well as a floor plan with all exhibitors' stands. Find information about the program or for arrival and departure, as well as accommodation in Cologne.

PLAN YOU VISIT

Find exhibitors by name, country and product groups and plan your visits with favourites, contacts, appointments and notes. Get information about the program. Keep track of interesting program dates with favourites to program dates.

NOTIFICATIONS

Get notification for short-term program changes and other short-term organizational changes directly to your device.

NETWORKING

Networking allows exhibitors and visitors to exchange contact information in the app before, during and after the event.

LEADTRACKING

Leadtracking allows the convenient export of their contacts made during the event.

DATA PROTECTION

The Mobile Guide requires appropriate permissions for "Add to address book" and "Add to Calendar" and will ask for that first time you use these functions. Contact data and appointments are stored at any time only local on your device.

HELP & SUPPORT

Send email for support to support@corussoft.de

IMPORTANT NOTICE BEFORE INSTALLATION

After installation the app will once download compressed data for exhibitors, extract and import them. Please make sure you have an adequate Internet connection and have some patience during this first import. This procedure can take up to one minute for the first time and should not be interrupted.

Kind + Jugend is THE international industry event in 2023. Leading manufacturers and brands, as well as numerous small and medium-sized specialist suppliers, show a wide range of products for baby and toddler outfitting. descriptionHtml:
The Mobile Guide for Kind + Jugend is the interactive event guide for the event from Kind + Jugend 03–05 September 2024

Kind + Jugend is the leading international trade fair for the baby and toddler sector. Here, wholesale and retail from all over the world meet manufacturers and producers from the segments Moving & Travelling, Furniture & Facility, Home Textiles & Decoration, Maternity & Kids Fashion, Toys & Education, Safety & Monitoring and Mom & Kids Care. Kind +Jugend is the perfect platform for global trade and the order business. Nowhere else in the world is there such a comprehensive display of what will be found in every child's bedroom tomorrow. It offers a comprehensive overview of the latest products, innovations and trends in the industry and is also a valuable networking platform for personal dialogue with the industry.

EXHIBITOR | PRODUCTS | INFORMATIONS
The app offers a detailed exhibitor and product directory as well as a floor plan with all exhibitors' stands. Find information about the program or for arrival and departure, as well as accommodation in Cologne.

PLAN YOU VISIT
Find exhibitors by name, country and product groups and plan your visits with favourites, contacts, appointments and notes. Get information about the program. Keep track of interesting program dates with favourites to program dates.

NOTIFICATIONS
Get notification for short-term program changes and other short-term organizational changes directly to your device.

NETWORKING
Get relevant networking suggestions based on your interests maintained in your profile and easily explore, expand and interact with your business network.
To complete your profile you can upload an image as your profile picture. If you don’t want to be a participant anymore you can delete your profile via the deletion function in your profile editing page.

MEETING-SCHEDULE
Schedule meetings with other networking participants to get together on site.

DATA PROTECTION
The Mobile Guide requires appropriate permissions for "Add to address book" and "Add to Calendar" and will ask for that first time you use these functions. Contact data and appointments are stored at any time only local on your device.

HELP & SUPPORT
Send email for support to kindundjugend@visitor.koelnmesse.de.

IMPORTANT NOTICE BEFORE INSTALLATION
After installation the app will once download compressed data for exhibitors, extract and import them. Please make sure you have an adequate Internet connection and have some patience during this first import. This procedure can take up to one minute for the first time and should not be interrupted.
